name: Fangamk
tagline: This is a language to describe a Snes era, RPG like game, a javascipt engine to play it and a pyqt application to make it.
body:
### Welcome to the Fangamk page!
 In this webpage I plan to show a small demo of the capabilities of the engine. 
## The Editor.py 
 Right now I'm still learning how to generate a binary to make the Editor easier to run. This will take some time - specially the OSX since this is the most obscure OS to me...
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
